    "hint": "",
    "noteLabel": "A note from Asobu",
    "noteHtml": "<div class=\"sp-wish\" style=\"margin:16px 0;\"><div class=\"sp-wish__body\"><img class=\"sp-wish__icon\" src=\"./mita/icon.png\" alt=\"Mitarai Asobu\"><div class=\"sp-wish__bubble-wrap\"><div class=\"sp-wish__bubble sp-wish__bubble--long\">Golden Week is… Mita Week!?　If you don’t have plans to go out with friends, come hang out with Yu instead!　Got nowhere to spend your paycheck? Well… spend it on me…　꒰꒱(⑅︎ᐢ￥ ᗜ ￥ᐢ ) hehe~　Even if you do have plans, all your free time belongs to Asobu~ 🕓　I’ll keep streaming non-stop for Jyumyou🤍</div></div></div></div>"
